    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that feels a bit loose over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
