    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a dedicated project or a donor vehicle for parts. The engine requires significant work to be roadworthy, and the body shows extensive wear, including deep scratches, several dents, and noticeable rust patches along the lower panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears and staining throughout. While it was once a reliable driver, it currently needs more investment than a standard tune-up can provide. We are offering it at a low price to reflect these necessary repairs.",
