    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly in absolutely flawless condition! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it garaged and sparkling clean, so it still looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this dream ride. If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
