      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive care. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed weekly. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete paper trail included. From the pristine alloy wheels to the untouched undercarriage, this car satisfies even the most discerning collector's standards. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
